R:\bigwedge^2\to\bigwedge^2
A=A^*,C=B^*,D=D^*
W^+=A-s/12,W^-=D-s/12
R=\begin{pmatrix}A&B\\C&D\end{pmatrix}
\begin{pmatrix}A&0\\0&D\end{pmatrix}-s/12=W,\mbox{the Weyl tensor}
